title: Question about Logitech G510 keyboard's League of legends  applet

embed.description: Imgur: The most awesome images on the Internet.

body: Hello, so recently my logitech G510 League of legends applet started displaying this (refer to image). So before I try to contact Logitech support, maybe anyone has and know if this maybe because of LoL updates interfering with applet (in logitech support it says that game updates can make applets not work). If anyone can help me I would apreciate.

replies.body: well i got also same prob {{item:3070}}

Since that keyboard was made and supported by Logitech, they're going to be the best source for troubleshooting that applet. I'm not entirely sure how that applet is working with League, so I'm not going to have much useful info =\ .
